{"lang": "ja_JP", "eventid": "act45side", "eventName": "安らかな譫言", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "SS-7", "avgTag": "戦闘前", "storyName": "永遠に輝くアルバム", "storyInfo": "祥子は夢の中で家族と幸せな時間を過ごしていた。「母」と散歩しながら思い出話に花を咲かせていたところ、仕事中のヴィグナ、アイリス、ベナと再会する。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "65_g6_sakikopianoroom", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_piano_start", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1941_1#6$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1941_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$victorianormal_loop", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上手になったわね、祥子ちゃん。", "name": "母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1941_1#6$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "そうかしら……", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1941_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子ちゃんが成長したことくらいわかるわ。お母さんだもの。", "name": "母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1941_1#5$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "お仕事がどんなに大変でも、ピアノだけはずっと頑張ってきたんでしょう？", "name": "母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1941_1#5$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "お母様……", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1941_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子ちゃん、外で色んな経験をしてきたのよね……", "name": "母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1941_1#5$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "練習の邪魔して悪いけど、ご飯ができたよ。", "name": "父"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "65_g5_sakikodininghall", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_dishes", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#11$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "美味しい……！", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#11$2"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1940_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "どうだ、お父さんなかなか上手だろう？", "name": "父"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1940_1#6$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1941_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子ちゃんは知らないでしょうけど……この味になるまで、何度も試食させられたのよ。", "name": "母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1941_1#5$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1940_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_plateplace", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "このサラダ、味見してみてほしい。", "name": "父"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1940_1#5$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#11$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ん――美味しいですわ！", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#11$2"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1940_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "なかなか上手だろう？　祥子が美味しいって言ってくれるように、何度もレシピを研究したんだぞ。", "name": "父"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1940_1#6$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子の好きなご飯、まだまだ作ってあるからな。さあ、どんどん食べてくれ！", "name": "父"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1940_1#6$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#11$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ええ！", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#11$2"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "65_g5_sakikodininghall", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "action": "shake", "random": "true", "power": 5.0, "times": 50.0, "duration": 0.4}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "う……うぅ……", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1941_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子ちゃん……？　祥子ちゃん！？", "name": "母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1941_1#3$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1940_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ど、どうしたんだ？", "name": "父"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1940_1#2$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "少し、食べすぎましたわ……", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "31_g3_mini12_farmland", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$saferoom_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1941_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子ちゃん、少しは良くなった……？", "name": "母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1941_1#7$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1940_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ごめんな、祥子。お父さんつい作りすぎちゃって……", "name": "父"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1940_1#3$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1941_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ほんと、清告さんったらいつもああなんだから……", "name": "母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1941_1#3$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1941_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "でもそれがあの人らしくて、可愛いところでもあるし……", "name": "母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1941_1#1$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子ちゃん、お父さんのこと許してあげてね？", "name": "母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1941_1#1$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "それは……", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "わたくしは……本当にお父様を許せるの？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "あの人とそっくりな顔をした人に、わたくしは何度も心を深く傷つけられた。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1941_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "お父さんはね、祥子ちゃんのことを愛してるのよ。", "name": "母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1941_1#5$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "――！", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1941_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "もちろん、お母さんも。", "name": "母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1941_1#6$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "二人のことを、心から愛してるわ。", "name": "母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1941_1#6$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "お母様、どうして急にそのようなことを……", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1941_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あなたが家を離れてから、昔のアルバムを見返すようになってね。", "name": "母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1941_1#1$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "生まれた時から、一歳、二歳、三歳……って。", "name": "母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1941_1#1$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "そのような幼い頃のこと、もう覚えていませんわ……", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1941_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "そうかもしれないわね。でも親にとっては、子供はずっと変わらずに、一番大切で、一番特別な存在なのよ。", "name": "母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1941_1#1$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "生まれたばかりのあなたは、手のひらが私の半分もなかったの。", "name": "母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1941_1#1$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "でも……ほら、今は私よりも大きくなったのね。", "name": "母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1941_1#1$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "母は祥子の手を取り、二人の手のひらをゆっくりと重ね合わせる。"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ひとりでに、祥子の指は母の手を強く握り締めていた。"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#13$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "お母様の手、すごく温かい……", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#13$2"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "これは本当にお母様の温もりなの？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "わたくしがいま感じているものは、嘘なんかではなくて――全て本物なの？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "どうしてこんなに温かいのに、こんなにも悲しいの？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1941_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ええ、お母さんはここにいるわ。", "name": "母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1941_1#6$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#8$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "お母様……", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#8$2"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1941_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "泣いていいのよ、祥子ちゃん。昔あなたが泣いてた時、こうやって慰めていたの。", "name": "母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1941_1#5$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#8$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……昔のわたくし、そんなに泣き虫でしたの？", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#8$2"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1941_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小さい頃はね。あの頃の祥子ちゃんは、よくキャンディひとつで泣いていたわ。", "name": "母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1941_1#5$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今はとても強い子になったけど、あの頃の祥子ちゃんは本当に泣き虫だったのよ。", "name": "母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1941_1#5$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "そ、そうだったかしら。そんな記憶、全くありませんわ……", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1941_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "うふふ、お母さんは嘘ついたりしないわ。", "name": "母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1941_1#6$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "では……お母様は、わたくしの高校の入学式を覚えてます？", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#1$2"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "中学三年生の時、母は病で亡くなった。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "存在しない記憶でも、起こっていない出来事でもいい。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "それでも今は、美しい答えを聞きたかった。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "自分に嘘をついてでも、美しい思い出を作り、美しい夢を見ていたかった。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1941_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ええ、もちろん覚えているわ。あの日は清告さんと祥子ちゃんの三人で、校門の前で記念写真を撮ったわね。", "name": "母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1941_1#6$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#13$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "そうでしたわね……懐かしいですわ。", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#13$2"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ふふっ、ねえお母様、もっとお話を聞かせてくださる？", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#1$2"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1941_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子ちゃん、今日はとても甘えん坊さんね。……それもそうね、久しぶりにお家に帰ってきてくれたんだもの。", "name": "母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1941_1#5$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#2$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "お家……", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#2$2"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "「家」という言葉は、一体いつからこんなにも馴染みのないものになってしまったの？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1941_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ふふっ。それならもっとお話ししちゃおうかしら。", "name": "母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1941_1#1$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ええと、どこから話そうかしら……", "name": "母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1941_1#1$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "でしたら、わたくしが生まれたときから、ずっと……", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#1$2"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1941_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ええ、はじめから話すわね。", "name": "母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1941_1#1$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "そうして、母と娘は肩を並べ、一歩ずつ歩調を合わせるように農地の間を歩いていた。まるで、いつまでもそのまま二人で歩いていけるかのように。"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "過去の美しかった時と変わらず、ゆったりと歩き、どこかで立ち止まることもない。"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "二人の手は、まるでお腹の中にいた頃のへその緒のように親子を繋いでいた。"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子――", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 5.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "false", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_enginerun", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "bse"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"channel": "bse", "volume": 0.3, "fadetime": 2.5}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "よかった。祥子、ちゃんと家に帰れてたんだね！", "name": "ヴィグナ"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ヴィグナさん、車の調子が何やらおかしいですわ！　いったん止めていただけませんこと？", "name": "アイリス"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "えっと……な、何これ！？　ロドスで習った操作方法と違うんだけど！？", "name": "ヴィグナ"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ダメ！　止められない！", "name": "ヴィグナ"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ぶつかってしまいますわ――", "name": "アイリス"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子さんたち、早く避けて――！", "name": "ベナ"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bse", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.1, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 5.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "false", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}